  "name": "Natural Scientist",
  "pfs": {
    "availability": "Standard",
    "subtype": "pfs",
    "type": "stat_block_section"
  },
  "schema_version": 1.4,
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Natural Scientist",
      "sections": [
        {
          "image": {
            "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png",
            "name": "Related Creatures",
            "type": "image"
          },
          "name": "Natural Sciences And Those Who Study Them",
          "sidebar_heading": "Related Creatures",
          "sidebar_type": "related_creatures",
          "sources": [
            {
              "link": {
                "alt": "NPC Core pg. 53",
                "aonid": 236,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "NPC Core pg. 53",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "NPC Core",
              "page": 53,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "There's a wide variety of things to explore and notate, and natural scientists want to document it all:  \n  \n **Astronomers** make detailed observations of the night sky.  \n **Biologists** may study the impact of civilization on wilderness areas.  \n **Botanists** may protect a newly discovered plant species.  \n **Chemists** may try to locate the source of a mysterious oil.  \n **Geologists** may rush to study a volcano.  \n **Zoologists** may try to track down a rare and elusive animal.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "NPC Core pg. 53",
            "aonid": 236,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "NPC Core pg. 53",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 53,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "If there's a mystery of nature that requires firsthand evidence to solve, natural scientists collect that data. They spend months documenting and observing events and creatures in the natural world before returning to their academies, labs, and royal studies.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
      "link": {
        "alt": "NPC Core pg. 53",
        "aonid": 236,
        "game-obj": "Sources",
        "name": "NPC Core pg. 53",
        "type": "link"
      },
      "name": "NPC Core",
      "page": 53,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
